According to SANParks 10 dead hippos were discovered earlier today in the Crocodile River. “Vets and scientists will be flown to the site to investigate and compile necropsy reports,” read a statement on SANParks’ social media platforms. SANParks also assured that no effort would be spared to get to the bottom of the gruesome discovery. ALSO WATCH: KNP visitor gets out of car to video lions